Summary
-------
GenomicTools: A flexible computational platform for analyzing genomic data.


Download
--------
The latest stable release can be downloaded from the website: 

http://code.google.com/p/ibm-cbc-genomic-tools


Installation
------------
Some tools require the GNU Scientific Library (GSL). After downloading the latest release of GenomicTools, follow these steps:

$ tar xvzf genomic-tools-VERSION.tgz 
$ cd gtools
$ make
$ sudo cp bin/* /usr/local/bin


